snippet.title: Dethroned - Release Date Reveal Trailer | Dark Fantasy Tactical Roguelike Army Builder
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2326050/Dethroned

Lead an army of fantasy creatures through a dark procedural open-world in Dethroned - a roguelike tactics auto-battler. Choose a mage, hone unique abilities, hunt for spells and artifacts. Explore an unpredictable world, win in tactical yet dynamic fights, and forge alliances to reclaim the throne.
